@startuml
title OpenTimezone request flow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "API Client\napp, website, script" as Client
participant "OpenTimezone API\nPOST /convert" as Api
participant "Conversion Logic\nTimezone.Core" as Core
participant ".NET TimeZoneInfo" as TimeZoneInfo
database "Linux tzdata" as TzData

Client -> Api : Send JSON request\n{ dateTime, fromTimezone, toTimezone }
Api -> Core : Validate and process request
Core -> TimeZoneInfo : Resolve and convert time zones
TimeZoneInfo -> TzData : Read time zone rules
TzData --> TimeZoneInfo : Offsets and DST rules
TimeZoneInfo --> Core : Converted Date/Time
Core --> Api : Converted Date/Time
Api --> Client : JSON response\n{ dateTime }
@enduml